about.description: Load data from WRF output files (NetCDF) to iris cubes
about.summary: Load data from WRF output files (NetCDF) to iris cubes

name: wrfcube
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "wrfcube" %}
{% set version = "1.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/mheikenfeld/{{name}}/archive/v{{version}}.tar.gz
  sha256: ade2b745f9cdbe9f6e3b5008d9ccdff335e5377820c2325b2bd6a19311ee6aed

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - numpy
    - scipy
    - iris 
    - xarray 
    - cf_units

test:
  imports:
    - wrfcube
  source_files:
    - wrfcube/tests/test_dummy.py
  requires:
    - pytest
  commands:
    - pytest wrfcube/tests
about:
  home: http://github.com/mheikenfeld/wrfcube
  license:  BSD-3-Clause 
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Load data from WRF output files (NetCDF) to iris cubes'

  description:  'Load data from WRF output files (NetCDF) to iris cubes'
  doc_url: http://wrfcube.readthedocs.io/
  dev_url: https://github.com/mheikenfeld/wrfcube

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - mheikenfeld
